{"tid":2339942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺悟被「理想」沖昏頭腦 在囚「勇武」悔不當初","createTime":"2020-12-25T05:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T00:37:21.000Z","uid":289157,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8c10489b3731c4d75a569ca1b15cbeab6aa2aebb","tid":2339942,"uid":289157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"係咪收左錢先講咁既野？<br />\n<br />\n對於參與違法示威入獄，「阿樂」表示當時衝動行事，悔不當初，希望通過媒體公開其經歷，告誡年輕人凡事三思而後行，切勿被「理念」沖昏頭腦，若要表達訴求，也應使用和平理性的方法，否則勢將步其後塵入獄：「勿待賠上自由才懂得後悔！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/2320372/日報-港聞-覺悟被-理想-沖昏頭腦-在囚-勇武-悔不當初\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F2320372%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A6%BA%E6%82%9F%E8%A2%AB-%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3-%E6%B2%96%E6%98%8F%E9%A0%AD%E8%85%A6-%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6-%E6%82%94%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E5%88%9D&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6d845cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F2320372%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A6%BA%E6%82%9F%E8%A2%AB-%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3-%E6%B2%96%E6%98%8F%E9%A0%AD%E8%85%A6-%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6-%E6%82%94%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E5%88%9D&h=ceaf2a1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/2320372/日報-港聞-覺悟被-理想-沖昏頭腦-在囚-勇武-悔不當初</a>"},{"pid":"ce6676ea4b214620256da82bd1a4509066accf98","tid":2339942,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"「和你sing」、「和你lunch」咁前期出現架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n⋯去年六月滿腔熱血參加和平示威，隨後將行動「升級」，但首趟參與「勇武抗爭」即被拘捕⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯不理家人勸阻參加「和你sing」、「和你lunch」等和平示威，但因沒法達成訴求，開始質疑「和理非」活動作用不大，加上受朋輩及網上資訊影響，決定訴諸激進，結果首次參與違法「勇武」行動即被拘捕⋯"},{"pid":"14036817a8654386e2a51bfeddc6b4bf1599a962","tid":2339942,"uid":11097,"l